                protocol_vk_patches (
                    minor,
                    patch,
                    recursion_scheduler_level_vk_hash,
                    recursion_node_level_vk_hash,
                    recursion_leaf_level_vk_hash,
                    recursion_circuits_set_vks_hash,
                    created_at
                )
            VALUES
                ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, NOW())
            ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING
